touVim
=====

1. https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim
2. http://sourabhbajaj.com/mac-setup/Vim/README.html to install The Ultimate vimrc
3. http://blog.decaywood.me/2016/09/15/vim/
4. http://www.iterm2.com/features.html
5. https://oli.me.uk/2013/06/29/equipping-vim-for-javascript/ 
   for Javascript, note to put .jshintrc into ~/.jshintrc, and add 'esversion': 6.
   this configuration will be applied globally.
6. brew install vim --with-lua --with-override-system-vi
7. YouCompleteMe plugin need CMake installed: brew install CMake
   Note: https://github.com/Valloric/YouCompleteMe
8. Vim smart search: TODO
9. 自動對齊

$ =G

10. delete lines
:startingline, last line d
:7,20 d
